slike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:56:01.000Z","msg":"科興，又名伏必中"},{"pid":"fa9d2fa98ad50d15762b331620c75b15f434d41b","tid":2428482,"uid":212623,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:56:03.000Z","msg":"無事，信政府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"167f1829db24b1ea1285b4b1ca4aa155615ab5f9","tid":2428482,"uid":249094,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:57:42.000Z","msg":"呢個係打BioNTech<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n總之唔關科興事，中国又然<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0680b8f8212ae242ccad25e186b910616b76e48","tid":2428482,"uid":126731,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:57:49.000Z","msg":"下世醒目d&nbsp;<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/gun.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"409efc11ec13179b64618031dd3034d6708ccb05","tid":2428482,"uid":156659,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:58:06.000Z","msg":"無事兒"},{"pid":"bd9a605d9a9e9ff53311104e9e6dd5724a2c8a98","tid":2428482,"uid":13663,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T14:58:54.000Z","msg":"4人接種疫苗後不適送院　其中1人留院觀察情況穩定<br />\n2021-03-01 HKT 22:43<br />\n 分享工具  facebook  twitter<br />\n<br />\n政府表示，昨日共有4人在銅鑼灣的中央圖書館疫苗接種中心，接種新型冠狀病毒疫苗後不適送院，全部情況穩定，其中1人需要留醫觀察。<br />\n<br />\n需要留醫的39歲男子接種疫苗後，出現眩暈及顫抖，被送往律敦治醫院留醫觀察。其餘3人分別是一名69歲女子，接種後血壓較高及身體無力；一名48歲男子出現血壓高及心悸；一名45歲男子接種後感到眩暈。<br />\n<br />\n今日共有約6400名市民接種第一劑新型冠狀病毒疫苗，自上月22日以來，累計超過27000人接種首劑疫苗。截至晚上8時，今日有超過15萬7000人在網上預約接種第一劑及第二劑疫苗，自上月23日以來，累計超過22萬8000人預約。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578185-20210301.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578185-20210301.htm&d=%2FJ3N9F3YYmWMkKlYGTVt1ytC6Bij9UJRoh6Gg3PlEes%3D&h=994c1a55\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1578185-20210301.htm&h=60d4c371\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1578185-20210301.htm</a>"},{"pid":"a2defbeb35dc93dcf0c7ec249306097cfd4c9e26","tid":2428482,"uid":173598,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:00:08.000Z","msg":"唔跟劇本謝主龍恩<br />\n國安法係時候要撚鳩呢4舊垃圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"83abf65f618a519c74ca041f3c3daf61522b75d7","tid":2428482,"uid":14983,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:00:19.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"cb3f293422453197a32174a111c9b08dd0745862","tid":2428482,"uid":176960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-01T15:22:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/vuVq9BW.gif\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FvuVq9BW.gif&h=5e910887&s={SIZE}\" />"}]}